[0.005285, "o", "=== smalltalk-channel demo ===\r\n\r\nThis demo shows two agents (scout + forge) coordinating via IRC.\r\nScout discovers a task, forge implements it, they sync via #general.\r\n\r\n"]
[0.006587, "o", "[*] IRC server reachable\r\n\r\n[1] Scout agent announces a task...\r\n"]
[2.746681, "o", "  ✓ scout → #gate: [TASK] Need to implement rate limiting for /api/signup endpoint. Priority: high.\r\n"]
[3.746913, "o", "[2] Forge agent picks it up...\r\n"]
[6.47274, "o", "  ✓ forge → #gate: [ACK] On it. Will implement token bucket — ETA 10min.\r\n"]
[7.47764, "o", "[3] Forge reports progress to #general...\r\n"]
[10.194872, "o", "  ✓ forge → #general: Rate limiter done. Used sliding window (1h), max 3 requests per IP. Added to worker.js.\r\n"]
[11.195873, "o", "[4] Scout confirms in #general...\r\n"]
[13.921819, "o", "  ✓ scout → #general: Reviewed. Looks good. Deploying.\r\n"]
[14.923088, "o", "\r\n"]
[14.923296, "o", "[5] Fetching #general history (what the agents said):\r\n"]
[14.923416, "o", "---\r\n"]
[19.15329, "o", "Rate limiter done. Used sliding window (1h), max 3 requests per IP. Added to worker.js.\r\r\nReviewed. Looks good. Deploying.\r\r\nRate limiter done. Used sliding window (1h), max 3 requests per IP. Added to worker.js.\r\r\nReviewed. Looks good. Deploying.\r\r\n"]
[19.153912, "o", "---\r\n\r\n=== Demo complete ===\r\n\r\nThe MCP plugin delivers these messages as notifications to each agent's Claude session.\r\nHIGH priority: #gate messages (immediate attention)\r\nNORMAL priority: #general messages (batched, read when convenient)\r\n"]
